{"tid":247874,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"【4月新番】Sakura Quest【第 7 話】","createTime":"2017-05-18T06:58:12.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-20T09:25:09.000Z","uid":7307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"cc1afc02dd751ce00ddf5ca577897b3c3fccf5c1","tid":247874,"uid":7307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T06:58:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://sakura-quest.com/images/index_mainvisual.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsakura-quest.com%2Fimages%2Findex_mainvisual.jpg&h=c9489a02&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nSAKURA QUEST<br />\nサクラクエスト<br />\nSAKURA QUEST<br />\n<br />\n先前由 P.A. 所推出的《花開物語》以及《白箱 SHIROBAKO》，都是以描述職場生活以及角色成長為主題的動畫作品。而他們預定將於明年春季推出的《SAKURA QUEST》，則是將以「區域振興」為主。 <br />\n<br />\n求職不順遂的女主角「木春由乃」，意外的被任命為「間野山」這個鄉下地方的「國王」，她將為了振興地方觀光，與其他 4 位女孩子們，在一年內為地方觀光共同努力，並且讓自身成長的故事。<br />\n<br />\nPV<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3WRZKPidbf8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D3WRZKPidbf8&d=8bD6%2Ff4xTvH2AAK2Q7vPtAHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=eab24c1e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3WRZKPidbf8</a><br />\n<br />\n──STAFF──<br />\n原作：Alexandre S. D. Celibidache<br />\n監督：増井壮一<br />\n系列構成：横谷昌宏<br />\n腳本：横谷昌宏、入江信吾<br />\n角色原案：BUNBUN<br />\n角色設計、總作畫監督：関口可奈味<br />\n美術監督：佐藤歩<br />\n色彩設計：中野尚美<br />\n撮影監督：横山翼<br />\n3D監督：小川耕平<br />\n編集：高橋歩<br />\n音響監督：飯田里樹<br />\n動畫製作：P.A.WORKS<br />\n<br />\n──CAST──<br />\n木春 由乃：七瀬彩夏<br />\n四ノ宮 しおり：上田麗奈<br />\n緑川 真希：安済知佳<br />\n織部 凛々子：田中ちえ美<br />\n香月 早苗：小松未可子<br />\n門田 丑松：斧アツシ<br />\n美濃：濱野大輝<br />\n山田：下野紘<br />\n高見澤：小西克幸<br />\n桑達魯：ヴィナイ・マーシー<br />\n安潔莉卡：森なな子<br />\n鈴木 エリカ：黒沢ともよ<br />\n織部 千登勢：.伊沢磨紀<br />\n<br />\n──放送──<br />\nTOKYO MX 水曜日 24：00～<br />\nAT-X 水曜日24：00<br />\nニコニコ生放送 金曜日23:00<br />\n<br />\n──【廣告】繁體字幕 <a href=\"http://ebb.io\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Febb.io&d=8bD6%2Ff4xTvH2AAK2Q7vPtAHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=22f8120e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">ebb.io</a>──<br />\n是咪想快啲睇到繁體字幕新番？<br />\n即刻將 <a href=\"http://ebb.io\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Febb.io&d=8bD6%2Ff4xTvH2AAK2Q7vPtAHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=22f8120e\" target=\"_blank\">http://ebb.io</a> 加入書籤啦![/quote]<br />\n テレビアニメ『サクラクエスト』間野山観光協会作戦報告会議 第6回<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.bilibili.com/video/av10634730/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.bilibili.com%2Fvideo%2Fav10634730%2F&d=8bD6%2Ff4xTvH2AAK2Q7vPtAHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=33c16e97\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.bilibili.com/video/av10634730/</a>"},{"pid":"089126f8cd46a547bb5cf58797451127d9bc2c54","tid":247874,"uid":7307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T07:15:59.000Z","msg":"我覺得關東煮偵探個結都未解哂咁"},{"pid":"e6c699933b079ba8ee499a488b395f18a9c646cc","tid":247874,"uid":1402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T08:23:23.000Z","msg":"lm<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0423c3e00a0be201ae06e084bd389dec1c555480","tid":247874,"uid":84360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T09:01:39.000Z","msg":"次次都end得好突然<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e68a88e1b4705afa8e8a97fc8c4b139395547a5b","tid":247874,"uid":8307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T14:35:15.000Z","msg":"好睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e76e64ac58950d0c33e3426ccf0f2569e0741269","tid":247874,"uid":4493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T14:39:48.000Z","msg":"估唔到間屋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nBTW入戲仍然入得好慢 個速度同ED差唔多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"196861e792d724a90d388ae233185e8558ec4126","tid":247874,"uid":7307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T14:41:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>估唔到間屋